The paper proposes a machine-learning approach to derive performance models from data, specifically focusing on queuing networks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with systems and control (cs.SY), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) in the context of building performance models.
